Description: Supports various geographical detector models for spatial stratified heterogeneity analysis. There are 9 kinds of 
             geographical detector models have been supported in gdverse, including native geographic detector(GD), optimal 
             parameters-based geographical detector(OPGD), geographically optimal zones-based heterogeneity model(GOZH), locally 
             explained heterogeneity model(LESH), spatial association detector(SPADE), interactive detector for spatial associations
             (IDSA), robust geographical detector(RGD), robust interactive detector(RID) and spatial rough set-based geographical 
             detector(SRSGD).
